description.plain:
Stella Donnelly is an Indie Pop singer-songwriter from Fremantle, Australia.

Born in WA and raised in Wales before moving back to Fremantle, she released her debut EP Thrush Metal in 2017. Her debut LP Beware of the Dogs was released in March 2019 via American independent label Secretly Canadian.

Before starting her solo career, she was member of bands Bells Rapids, Boat Show, Human Buoy, and Too Short.
